headline: Biogen, UCB Present Positive Phase 3 Results for Lupus Drug Candidate at EULAR 2025
summary: Biogen Inc. (NASDAQ:BIIB) is one of the 11 most profitable NASDAQ stocks to buy now. On June 12, UCB and Biogen presented additional detailed results from the Phase 3 PHOENYCS GO study, evaluating dapirolizumab pegol (DZP), which is a novel Fc-free anti-CD40L drug candidate.
